8.11 DUIM-Gadgets Module

node-parents

Generic function

Summary

Returns the parents of the specified node in a tree control.

Signature

node-parents tree-node => parents

Arguments

tree-node
An instance of type <tree-node>.

Values

parents
An instance of type <sequence>.

Library

duim-gadgets

Module

duim-gadgets

Description

Returns the parents of tree-node in a tree control.

See also

node-children, page 618

<tree-node>, page 690
